uding gilt market and eurobond market indexlinked bonds and money markets it typic standard life investments limited is a privately owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to individuals and institutions it manages separate clientfocused equity fixedincome and balanced portfolios the firm launches and manages equity fixed income and balanced mutual funds hedge funds pension funds property pension fund property funds money market funds and typically oeic funds for its clients it invests in the public equity fixed income and real estate markets across the globe for its fixed income portion the firm invests in government and corporate bonds including gilt market and eurobond market indexlinked bonds and money markets it typically invests in growth stocks of smallcap midcap and largecap companies the firm employs a fundamental analysis to create its portfolios it conducts inhouse research to make its investments it also invests in real estate in united kingdom the firm was founded in  and is based in edinburgh scotland with additional offices in sydney australia dublin ireland toronto ontario los angeles california new york city boston massachusetts seoul south korea and singapore standard life investments limited operates as a subsidiary of standard life investments holdings limited detailed description one george street haymarket terraceedinburgh  eh llunited kingdomfounded in  phone     fax     wwwstandardlifeinvestmentscom key executives for standard life investments limited mr norman keith skeoch chief executive officer and executive director age  mr colin martin clark head of global client group and executive director age  mr colin richard walklin bsc fca finance director age  mr william regnar littleboy operations director and director mr choon wah wong chief executive officer of singapore and head of asia pacific real estate compensation as of fiscal year  standard life investments limited key developments standard life investments limi